Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:36.68,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(250,250)}Kosuru mabuta manin no densha no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:43.78,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(250,250)}Marude dareka no jinsei no extra mitai
