Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.85,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(250,250)}My life itsu no hi ni ka Colorful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:14.44,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(250,250)}Iro no nai ame ga itsuka niji wo egaku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:20.69,OP ROMANJI,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(250,250)}My life donna iro no end roll
